title: 473.701 DEFINITIONS.
text:
As used in sections 473.701 to 473.716, the terms defined in this section have the meanings given them.
"District" means the Metropolitan Mosquito Control District created by section 473.702.
"Commission," unless otherwise specified, means the Metropolitan Mosquito Control Commission created by section 473.702.
"Commissioner" means a member of the commission.
